$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_short_pattern

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_short_pattern -  Returns the short pattern for the given pattern string.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_short_pattern(string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the pattern to get the short for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the short pattern

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/pattern_compiler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Returns the short pattern for the given pattern string.   The short pattern
is the message which is shown to the players.
.EP

